					<msContents class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85070287" rend="visible">
						<summary>Sefer mitsṿot gadol of Moses ben Jacob of Coucy. </summary>
						<textLang mainLang="he"/>
						<msItem rend="visible" class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85070287">
							<locus from="1r" to="377v"/>
							<title xml:lang="en">Sefer mitsṿot gadol </title>
							<title xml:lang="he">ספר מצוות גדול </title>
							<author key="http://viaf.org/viaf/88359425">
								<persName key="http://viaf.org/viaf/88359425" xml:lang="en">Moses ben Jacob, of Coucy, active 13th century </persName>
								<persName key="http://viaf.org/viaf/88359425" xml:lang="he">משה בן יעקב, מקוצי </persName>
							</author>
							<note>
								<p>The paragraphs 340-351 of mitsṿot lo᾿ ta῾aseh are missing. </p>
								<p>There is an index to the occurence of the mitsṿot in the weekly readings on folio 116r. </p>
							</note>
							<colophon xml:lang="he">כתבתי אני <name type="person" role="scribe">יוסף בר אברהם פריר</name> ז"ל מצות לא תעשה של הרב רבנו משה דקושי ז"ל והשלמתיו בשבעה עשר ימים לחדש מרחשון השם למען שמו יזכהו להגות בו אני וזרעי וזרע זרעי שנת<date when="1404" calendar="Hebrew"> קס"ד</date>. <locus n="115v"/>
							</colophon>
						</msItem>
					</msContents>
					<physDesc rend="visible">
						<p>Parchment codex of the 15th century.</p>
						<objectDesc form="codex">
							<supportDesc material="perg">
								<extent>377 folios <dimensions unit="mm" type="leaf">
										<height>320</height>
										<width>250</width>
									</dimensions>
									<dimensions type="written" unit="mm">
										<height>210</height>
										<width>160</width>
									</dimensions>
								</extent>
								<foliation>
									<p>377 folios (+ 3 unfoliated modern paper flyleaves at the beginning and at the end). </p>
								</foliation>
								<collation>
									<p>Currently 50 quires: i-xiv8 (folios 1-112); xv3 (folios 113-115); xvi8-3 (folios 116-120); xvii-l8 (folios 121-377). </p>
								</collation>
								<condition>
									<p>Imperfect at the beginning and at the end. </p>
									<p>Foxed. </p>
								</condition>
							</supportDesc>
							<layoutDesc>
								<layout columns="1 " ruledLines="33" writtenLines="33">
									<p>Uniform layout. Last line written outside the ruling. </p>
									<p>Pricking and hard-point ruling visible. </p>
									<p>Hair-side and fleash-side of the folios distinguishable. </p>
									<p>Occasional marginal notes. </p>
									<p>Chapter initials and numbers given in larger characters. </p>
								</layout>
							</layoutDesc>
						</objectDesc>
						<handDesc hands="1">
							<summary>Sefardi semi-cursive of the 15th century.<name type="person" role="scribe"> Yosef bar Avraham Pereir </name>(?): inscribed in the colophon: folio 115v. </summary>
							<handNote script="Hebrew" scope="sole"/>
						</handDesc>
						<additions>
							<p>Latin and English descriptions of the manuscript pasted on a paper flyleaf at the beginning of the volume, [iii recto]. </p>
						</additions>
						<bindingDesc>
							<binding>
								<p>BM in-house. </p>
								<p>Spine title: 'Moses of Coucy. Sefer Miswoth Gadol. Hebrew. Brit. Mus. Harley 5700.'</p>
							</binding>
						</bindingDesc>
